# FMD: see AGENTS.md

This project uses FMD via a **zero-footprint pointer** at `AGENTS.md` in the repo root. Read it first; it pins FMD 1.14.0 and tells you how to fetch the canonical engine from https://github.com/delatorrecj/fmd at tag `v1.14.0`.

Do not duplicate FMD rules in this file. If the workflow changes, update the pointer or re-run `scripts/init.ps1` (Windows) or `scripts/init.sh` (Linux/macOS) from the FMD source repo.